  "title": "IT Helpdesk (SI Environment) – Urgent Hiring",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Manage user IDs, access rights, and role-based quota controls.</li><li>Maintain IT documentation, filing systems, and access logs.</li><li>Monitor and control USB and external device usage.</li><li>Document and report IT incidents and support resolution activities.</li><li>Prepare monthly IT reports and maintain system maintenance and release logs.</li><li>Perform routine server maintenance and periodic hardware/software checks.</li><li>Support system releases, projects, and ad-hoc IT tasks.</li><li>Coordinate system maintenance and power shutdown/startup activities.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in IT or related field.</li><li>Basic knowledge of IT operations, security controls, and system maintenance.</li><li>Preferably at least two (2) years of experience in IT support or Helpdesk operations.<br /></li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please send in your resume to <a href=\"mailto:it@talenttradersg.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>it@talenttradersg.com</strong></a><br /></p><p>EA License No: 13C6305</p><p>Reg. No.: R24120209 (GAN CHYE SHEN)<br /></p><p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
